// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1457 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ada55535-17c9-5157-9b6b-ce325122ca60

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
